    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/76d4caeb7cff8eb310043ac686e38c38.webp?t=1744245709\" width=605 height=63 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Freedom!</h2> You are not limited to four or eight directions. Just naturally use your mouse for moving Marvin. This opens limitless possibilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/e0e3f0a324f5625efbf9d16114e05092.poster.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/e0e3f0a324f5625efbf9d16114e05092.webm?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/e0e3f0a324f5625efbf9d16114e05092.mp4?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight with your own punches.</h2> Punching in-game requires real punching, Swing your mouse hard like a motion controller!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/af626fcafee8c62622e15d70a86fa1be.poster.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/af626fcafee8c62622e15d70a86fa1be.webm?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/af626fcafee8c62622e15d70a86fa1be.mp4?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You even can break walls!</h2>Headbang!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/b08e8751cf346ab2e706d3c8918a67f8.poster.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=162 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/b08e8751cf346ab2e706d3c8918a67f8.webm?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/b08e8751cf346ab2e706d3c8918a67f8.mp4?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Minigames.</h2> We've wanted to fully utilize the mouse controls. There are lots of fun mini games here. Lots of.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/adfb98d3888f3dea051261d3674e99d1.poster.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/adfb98d3888f3dea051261d3674e99d1.webm?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/adfb98d3888f3dea051261d3674e99d1.mp4?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story.</h2> The story is told through animated cutscenes which strengthened with a long soundtrack. And, it isn't a short story.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/dd4fc071b0fac41efd541194955fad1f.poster.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/dd4fc071b0fac41efd541194955fad1f.webm?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/dd4fc071b0fac41efd541194955fad1f.mp4?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soundtrack.</h2> Almost each level features cutscenes and characters which has their own emotions and story. So while being consistent, they each feature different music. This also applies to the fights. There is a long and carefully composed soundtrack.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/60112ce858e4a9df375b704a5e237245.poster.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/60112ce858e4a9df375b704a5e237245.webm?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/60112ce858e4a9df375b704a5e237245.mp4?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels.</h2> The game's length is more than 60 levels including prologues &amp; epilogues. Each of them features a different experience while maintaining the main flow of the storyline.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dick Hunt.</h2> The game is also a western shooter. For some time of course. You can also play the old cowboy &quot;Dick Hunt&quot;.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/354ce3399f1e9d9a1e1e0e618dbf6547.poster.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/354ce3399f1e9d9a1e1e0e618dbf6547.webm?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/354ce3399f1e9d9a1e1e0e618dbf6547.mp4?t=1744245709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/bf154e056d7f59b8e8f5fefbccf248a0.webp?t=1744245709\" width=605 height=63 /></span><br>Do you know how does an arcade machine work? There are creatures living inside it. Processor workers, pixel illuminators, garbage collectors, and actors. When the machine is turned on, they go to work, and when it's shut down, they return their home. There was a game called &quot;Mashed Potato!&quot;. Have you heard about it? There was a potato, fleeing away from bricks as long as possible. It was entertaining. Its lead actor was Marvin the Potato. He had big dreams. But things never go as dreamed...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/857a9d0be90ff77b8e35361453ebe0af.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2296500/extras/e1655362180989f601ff92fc310da1d1.avif?t=1744245709\" width=600 height=160 /></span>",
